  "detailed_description": "Storybook of Tactics mixes deck building gameplay with a colorful auto battler. As a commander, you can feel the tactical depth with equipping items, obtaining powers, and placing units of your evolving army to crush multiple waves of enemies and powerful bosses.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless replayability</h2>Randomly generated maps across multiple locations, a selection of leaders with unique powers, and risk-and-reward in-game events ensure that surprise awaits at every corner.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/75400177fceba3368a706775df6b5764.poster.avif?t=1742578631\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/75400177fceba3368a706775df6b5764.webm?t=1742578631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tactical yet accessible auto battler</h2>New players to the genre can quickly understand the rules of making a successful army, and loosing a battle doesn't require a frustrating restart. Auto battler veterans can fight for flawless victories with more difficult map modifiers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/46b97c3b7d6e06e3a88492d3b11053e7.poster.avif?t=1742578631\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/46b97c3b7d6e06e3a88492d3b11053e7.webm?t=1742578631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Flexible playstyles</h2>You are free to experiment with the available tactics and choose the right one for your style of play, the rules of the map and the type of enemies. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/ee37829c251fc8a9f21ec86de965faf7.poster.avif?t=1742578631\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/ee37829c251fc8a9f21ec86de965faf7.webm?t=1742578631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Colorful 2D art</h2>From animations & UI, diverse locations, appealing visuals of bosses, to design of enemies and skills - everything is colorful and pleasant. But don't let your guard down! <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/4fdabae2adcf0239aeae2975fca1f01b.poster.avif?t=1742578631\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/4fdabae2adcf0239aeae2975fca1f01b.webm?t=1742578631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Storybook of Tactics mixes deck building gameplay with a colorful auto battler. As a commander, you can feel the tactical depth with equipping items, obtaining powers, and placing units of your evolving army to crush multiple waves of enemies and powerful bosses.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless replayability</h2>Randomly generated maps across multiple locations, a selection of leaders with unique powers, and risk-and-reward in-game events ensure that surprise awaits at every corner.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/75400177fceba3368a706775df6b5764.poster.avif?t=1742578631\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/75400177fceba3368a706775df6b5764.webm?t=1742578631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tactical yet accessible auto battler</h2>New players to the genre can quickly understand the rules of making a successful army, and loosing a battle doesn't require a frustrating restart. Auto battler veterans can fight for flawless victories with more difficult map modifiers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/46b97c3b7d6e06e3a88492d3b11053e7.poster.avif?t=1742578631\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/46b97c3b7d6e06e3a88492d3b11053e7.webm?t=1742578631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Flexible playstyles</h2>You are free to experiment with the available tactics and choose the right one for your style of play, the rules of the map and the type of enemies. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/ee37829c251fc8a9f21ec86de965faf7.poster.avif?t=1742578631\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/ee37829c251fc8a9f21ec86de965faf7.webm?t=1742578631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Colorful 2D art</h2>From animations & UI, diverse locations, appealing visuals of bosses, to design of enemies and skills - everything is colorful and pleasant. But don't let your guard down! <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/4fdabae2adcf0239aeae2975fca1f01b.poster.avif?t=1742578631\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/4fdabae2adcf0239aeae2975fca1f01b.webm?t=1742578631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
